{"tid":1136064,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人生就係由一次又一次既肚痾捱過黎","createTime":"2019-05-02T17:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T18:26:13.000Z","uid":204916,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"637b2adff3a9402e415920621ded40401c530314","tid":1136064,"uid":204916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T17:55:23.000Z","msg":"你地又點會諗到自己將來會肚痾？呢個就係意外。<br />\n你地又點會諗到自己會痾幾耐？呢個就係驚喜。<br />\n而你地又會因放得返屁而快樂，呢個叫幸福 ，而唔係濕鳩小確幸！嗰種苦盡甘來既感受，難以忘記！<br />\n肚屙過程既起承轉合咪就係好似人生咁，變幻莫測...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔打啦，繼續努力屙，努力係人生中留下屎跡！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：短時間接觸六次廁所板，菊花畀火燒緊。"},{"pid":"cc969aa7c584c0f0f05f13c07a831a3dfaab8023","tid":1136064,"uid":204916,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:00:52.000Z","msg":"而放屁放到尾放埋爛屎，咁又係另一種體會"},{"pid":"d5c41b0fb886f8badd6e45ca9f03ab3f11ecbe96","tid":1136064,"uid":204916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:07:31.000Z","msg":"洗底褲先"},{"pid":"168887ec3e77b8566dc6a96f09c5380b8201a5a2","tid":1136064,"uid":60665,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:09:36.000Z","msg":"7:00, 8:30, 9:30, 10:30, 11:15, 12:00, 1:10, 2:20, 3:05, 4:10, 5:50, 6:15, 7:10, 9:00, 10:01, 10:49, 11:45, 12:30, 1:30, 6:35, 9:20, 12:20, 1:30, 2:30, 5:30, 6:09, 6:32, 06:55, 7:15, 7:35, 8:08, 8:35, 9:05, 9:30, 9:55"},{"pid":"7ea3282159e943d786291adbab22787a4054203c","tid":1136064,"uid":139113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:10:20.000Z","msg":"我都試過 成日肚all 真係好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a728122cbcbf4d91aceae6db2f13d7846527d8b5","tid":1136064,"uid":204916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"到底睡意可唔可以麻醉我既肚痾呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif